00:59:36,820 --> 00:59:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] nego će reći kakve to veze ima s tim šta si ti govorila,

500
00:59:40,400 --> 00:59:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] tak da mislim da isto ovisi o percepciji,

501
00:59:44,960 --> 00:59:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] za mene je to bio taj jedan od tih trenutaka,

502
00:59:47,539 --> 00:59:50,360
[SPEAKER_01] još jedan trenutak je bio,

503
00:59:50,360 --> 00:59:54,019
[SPEAKER_01] prije nego što sam odlučila se seliti u Portugal,

504
00:59:54,019 --> 00:59:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] jedan poznanik,

505
00:59:56,679 --> 01:00:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo osoba koju sam upoznala možda dva put,

506
01:00:02,300 --> 01:00:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] sam vidjela tu osobu taj tjedan,

507
01:00:04,860 --> 01:00:10,780
[SPEAKER_01] i na kraju tjedna nas je zvao na jedan kao roštilj kod sebe,

508
01:00:10,780 --> 01:00:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] neću sad govoriti detalje jer će se onda znati,

509
01:00:14,039 --> 01:00:15,900
[SPEAKER_01] ali došli smo na roštilj,

510
01:00:15,900 --> 01:00:17,900
[SPEAKER_01] moja prijateljica je bila kolegica njihova

511
01:00:17,900 --> 01:00:19,460
[SPEAKER_01] i ona dovela me onak nedjelja,

512
01:00:19,460 --> 01:00:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] bila popodne, ljeto,

513
01:00:20,900 --> 01:00:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] i ta osoba se fotografirala s nama na polaroid,

514
01:00:26,099 --> 01:00:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo držali taj polaroid,

515
01:00:28,000 --> 01:00:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] taj polaroid se nije još napravio,

516
01:00:29,940 --> 01:00:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] on je doživio srčani udar pred svim svojim prijateljima

517
01:00:33,039 --> 01:00:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] i mi smo stajali ispred hitne službe,

518
01:00:36,960 --> 01:00:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači ne znam,

519
01:00:37,739 --> 01:00:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] nadam se da nisi nikad doživio oživljavanje,

520
01:00:40,960 --> 01:00:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali taj šok da to oživljavanje traje 45 minuta,

521
01:00:46,420 --> 01:00:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] da to nije ono 5 minuta ko na filmu,

522
01:00:49,960 --> 01:00:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda proglašenje,

523
01:00:51,099 --> 01:00:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego stajanje 45 minuta

524
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] i gledanje kako se to događa,

525
01:00:57,420 --> 01:01:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] i evo, tu je meni bio,

526
01:01:01,260 --> 01:01:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] i taj isto malo je suludi osjećaj isto,

527
01:01:04,900 --> 01:01:09,340
[SPEAKER_01] 45 minuta se oživljava osobu i nekako misliš,

528
01:01:09,340 --> 01:01:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] pa dobro, mislim, ne bi to radili 45 minuta ako neće preživjet,

529
01:01:13,699 --> 01:01:15,519
[SPEAKER_01] i nažalost nije,

530
01:01:15,519 --> 01:01:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek je umro tamo,

531
01:01:17,980 --> 01:01:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] i ja se sjećam da je meni taj trenutak bio

532
01:01:20,920 --> 01:01:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] kao neki,

533
01:01:22,559 --> 01:01:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] kao nekako ono rastvaranje

534
01:01:25,699 --> 01:01:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] zastora,

535
01:01:28,059 --> 01:01:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] onak,

536
01:01:29,059 --> 01:01:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] zašto se ja brinem,

537
01:01:31,400 --> 01:01:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] da li ću napraviti dobru stvar,

538
01:01:37,940 --> 01:01:39,739
[SPEAKER_01] kao da li je to dobra odluka,

539
01:01:39,739 --> 01:01:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] da idem ili trebam ostati,

540
01:01:41,579 --> 01:01:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] ili ovo,

541
01:01:42,039 --> 01:01:44,139
[SPEAKER_01] život se događa,

542
01:01:44,139 --> 01:01:45,280
[SPEAKER_01] smrt se događa,

543
01:01:45,280 --> 01:01:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] mogu sutra umrijeti,

544
01:01:46,960 --> 01:01:48,219
[SPEAKER_01] ne mora to biti nužno,

545
01:01:48,219 --> 01:01:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] nije to ono jolo,

546
01:01:49,440 --> 01:01:52,179
[SPEAKER_01] joj moram raditi svaku ludu stvar koja mi padne na pamet,

547
01:01:52,179 --> 01:01:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] nego

548
01:01:52,679 --> 01:01:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] pogledaj što je bitno,

549
01:01:56,880 --> 01:01:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] osjeti što je tebi bitno,

550
01:01:59,639 --> 01:02:01,900
[SPEAKER_01] i to je bio neki ono poticaj,

551
01:02:01,900 --> 01:02:02,940
[SPEAKER_01] čekaj,

552
01:02:02,940 --> 01:02:04,820
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi umiru,

553
01:02:04,820 --> 01:02:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi umiru,

554
01:02:06,500 --> 01:02:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] a ti se sad brineš,

555
01:02:07,460 --> 01:02:08,699
[SPEAKER_01] šta će netko misliti,

556
01:02:08,699 --> 01:02:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti odeš i za tri mjeseca se vratiš iz Portugala,

557
01:02:11,480 --> 01:02:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer eto, nije to ipak bila tvoja odluka,

558
01:02:13,460 --> 01:02:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] taj, isto,

559
01:02:14,579 --> 01:02:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] strah od pogreške,

560
01:02:15,840 --> 01:02:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] bojim se pogriješiti,

561
01:02:17,559 --> 01:02:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer šta će grad reći,

562
01:02:19,699 --> 01:02:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] selo reći,

563
01:02:20,460 --> 01:02:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] šta će netko misliti,

564
01:02:21,679 --> 01:02:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] evo nje je prekinula s dečkom,

565
01:02:23,199 --> 01:02:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] pa se celila,

566
01:02:23,900 --> 01:02:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa se opet vratila,

567
01:02:24,960 --> 01:02:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] pa mislim opet sam se vratila,

568
01:02:26,920 --> 01:02:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] sam se vratila nakon pet godina,

569
01:02:28,480 --> 01:02:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] netko će uvijek imat svoje mišljenje,

570
01:02:31,719 --> 01:02:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo,

571
01:02:33,159 --> 01:02:35,280
[SPEAKER_01] to su bili neki trenuci u mom životu,

572
01:02:35,280 --> 01:02:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ja onak samo,

573
01:02:36,260 --> 01:02:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] kada sam samo propala u sebe,

574
01:02:40,039 --> 01:02:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] ishvatila niš drugo nije bitno,

575
01:02:42,699 --> 01:02:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego tvoj taj neki glasić,

576
01:02:45,500 --> 01:02:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] osjećaj,

577
01:02:46,440 --> 01:02:49,639
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da jednom kad se tome otvorimo,

578
01:02:49,639 --> 01:02:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] da počnu dolaziti ti znakovi,

579
01:02:52,920 --> 01:02:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] tad sam ja postala najviše povezana sa duhovnim,

580
01:02:56,880 --> 01:03:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno sam imala osjećaj da svaki sljedeći trenutak,

581
01:03:00,679 --> 01:03:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] u toj godini,

582
01:03:01,619 --> 01:03:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] moje selitbe,

583
01:03:03,059 --> 01:03:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] da mi je

584
01:03:03,880 --> 01:03:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] nešto govorio,

585
01:03:06,480 --> 01:03:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] psiholozi će reći

586
01:03:08,059 --> 01:03:09,260
[SPEAKER_01] confirmation bias,

587
01:03:09,260 --> 01:03:10,360
[SPEAKER_01] ti si htjela ići,

588
01:03:10,360 --> 01:03:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa si onda nalazila razloge da ideš,

589
01:03:12,460 --> 01:03:12,980
[SPEAKER_01] ok,

590
01:03:12,980 --> 01:03:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] za mene je to bio znak.

591
01:03:15,619 --> 01:03:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimljivo je što smo

592
01:03:21,519 --> 01:03:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] mi svi svjesni kao svoje smrti,

593
01:03:24,360 --> 01:03:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali realno nismo je baš svjesni.

594
01:03:27,079 --> 01:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nije ne trebamo biti.

595
01:03:29,000 --> 01:03:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Misliš,

596
01:03:29,880 --> 01:03:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] super su mi ove priče bile by the way,

597
01:03:33,300 --> 01:03:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] malo su tragične bile,

598
01:03:35,440 --> 01:03:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali su bile upećatljive.

599
01:03:38,199 --> 01:03:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ti misliš,

600
01:03:40,900 --> 01:03:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ljudi je svjesno

601
01:03:43,199 --> 01:03:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] da uopće

602
01:03:45,340 --> 01:03:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] postoji

603
01:03:46,719 --> 01:03:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] odnos sa samim sobom?

604
01:03:48,440 --> 01:03:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko su ljudi upušta u tako nešto?

605
01:03:51,900 --> 01:03:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš,

606
01:03:52,980 --> 01:03:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] mi razumijemo,

607
01:03:54,480 --> 01:03:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] ok, imam nekakav odnos sa evom,

608
01:03:57,079 --> 01:03:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] imam ženu,

609
01:03:58,500 --> 01:03:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] imam djecu,

610
01:03:59,159 --> 01:03:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] imam što god,

611
01:03:59,900 --> 01:04:02,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali mislim da malo ljudi

612
01:04:02,159 --> 01:04:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] percipira to da,

613
01:04:04,179 --> 01:04:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

614
01:04:04,480 --> 01:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] možeš ostati sam sa sobom

615
01:04:07,000 --> 01:04:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] i imati nekakav odnos sa sobom.

616
01:04:08,539 --> 01:04:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nije on samo kad si sam,

617
01:04:10,579 --> 01:04:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] ne presta je on onda,

618
01:04:13,059 --> 01:04:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] nego postoji kad si okružen s drugim ljudima.

619
01:04:18,099 --> 01:04:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i utječe

620
01:04:19,300 --> 01:04:20,860
[SPEAKER_01] na odnos s drugim.

621
01:04:20,860 --> 01:04:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] E sad,

622
01:04:22,639 --> 01:04:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] to pitanje koliko,

623
01:04:24,219 --> 01:04:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu reći koliko,

624
01:04:27,039 --> 01:04:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je isto stvar

625
01:04:28,239 --> 01:04:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] okruženja,

626
01:04:29,960 --> 01:04:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da,

627
01:04:30,699 --> 01:04:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] kak da kažem,

628
01:04:34,059 --> 01:04:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] prirodno,

629
01:04:35,019 --> 01:04:37,199
[SPEAKER_01] dobro nije to riječ,

630
01:04:37,199 --> 01:04:37,820
[SPEAKER_01] prirodno,

631
01:04:37,820 --> 01:04:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali nekako

632
01:04:38,980 --> 01:04:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] pretpostavit ćemo

633
01:04:40,519 --> 01:04:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] da si ti okružen ljudima

634
01:04:42,380 --> 01:04:43,780
[SPEAKER_01] koji su svjesni

635
01:04:43,780 --> 01:04:45,980
[SPEAKER_01] odnosa sa samim sobom,

636
01:04:45,980 --> 01:04:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja okružena ljudima

637
01:04:47,179 --> 01:04:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji su svjesni

638
01:04:47,940 --> 01:04:49,320
[SPEAKER_01] odnosa sa samim sobom.

639
01:04:49,320 --> 01:04:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da isto tako,

640
01:04:50,579 --> 01:04:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] naša svijest o tome

641
01:04:52,639 --> 01:04:53,719
[SPEAKER_01] utječe na ljude

642
01:04:53,719 --> 01:04:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] oko nas,

643
01:04:54,699 --> 01:04:55,780
[SPEAKER_01] kad jedna osoba

644
01:04:55,780 --> 01:04:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] u društvu krene

645
01:04:56,480 --> 01:04:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] na psihoterapiju,

646
01:04:57,500 --> 01:04:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda jednom spomene

647
01:04:58,719 --> 01:05:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] kako joj je nešto pomoglo

648
01:05:01,179 --> 01:05:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] na psihoterapiji,

649
01:05:02,800 --> 01:05:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda druga osoba

650
01:05:03,840 --> 01:05:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] kaže kao,

651
01:05:04,380 --> 01:05:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] aha,

652
01:05:04,619 --> 01:05:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] pa možda bi mogao

653
01:05:05,820 --> 01:05:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja otići,

654
01:05:06,500 --> 01:05:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] pa ode,

655
01:05:07,519 --> 01:05:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

656
01:05:07,840 --> 01:05:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam vidjela

657
01:05:08,539 --> 01:05:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] da od kad sam ja

658
01:05:09,719 --> 01:05:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] otišla na psihoterapiju,

659
01:05:10,860 --> 01:05:11,659
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo sad sve moje

660
01:05:11,659 --> 01:05:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] prijateljice idu na psihoterapiju,

661
01:05:13,019 --> 01:05:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] ne nužno zbog mene,

662
01:05:14,019 --> 01:05:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ja njih uvela u to,

663
01:05:15,960 --> 01:05:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je taj neki val.

664
01:05:18,079 --> 01:05:22,199
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da moja percepcija će možda biti malo iskrivljena,

665
01:05:22,199 --> 01:05:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovo što ti kažeš da je malo ljudi svjesno toga.

666
01:05:24,900 --> 01:05:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] Slažem se i sa tvojom izjavom,

667
01:05:29,179 --> 01:05:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] a opet moje iskustvo je da su ljudi svjesni na neki način da sebi rade nešto.

668
01:05:38,960 --> 01:05:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] Možda ne znaju nazvati to riječima,

669
01:05:41,519 --> 01:05:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] možda ne znaju reći da li je to sad odnos,

670
01:05:43,480 --> 01:05:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] moj odnos sa mnom i kako ću seba pobrinut za sebe,

671
01:05:48,280 --> 01:05:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] možda nemaju taj vokabular

672
01:05:49,900 --> 01:05:53,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili nisu još svjesni toga da bi to tako nazvali,

673
01:05:53,159 --> 01:05:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali ljudi kažu ono da, pa onda sam si,

674
01:05:56,559 --> 01:05:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] baš sam glupa,

675
01:05:59,340 --> 01:06:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] znam se često ljutit na sebe,

676
01:06:02,519 --> 01:06:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi će to reći,

677
01:06:03,500 --> 01:06:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] reći će ono jedna sam pogriješio

678
01:06:06,119 --> 01:06:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] i onda sam se, kako sam se izmaltretirao,

679
01:06:09,420 --> 01:06:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] lupo sam glavam u zid,

680
01:06:10,659 --> 01:06:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] sam htio lupat,

681
01:06:11,780 --> 01:06:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] koliko sam se izmrcvario oko te pogreške.

682
01:06:15,059 --> 01:06:19,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi će nekad imati tu svijest da to nije nešto što bi tako trebalo biti.

683
01:06:19,679 --> 01:06:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ili će reći ono dobro, ok, pogriješio sam,

684
01:06:22,380 --> 01:06:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] zašto sam morao cijeli projekt baciti u smeće,

685
01:06:25,380 --> 01:06:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam pogriješio.

686
01:06:26,400 --> 01:06:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kažnjavam se.

687
01:06:28,960 --> 01:06:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] I onda će možda, ja mislim,

688
01:06:30,639 --> 01:06:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] na taj način,

689
01:06:32,000 --> 01:06:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] sa strane,

690
01:06:35,079 --> 01:06:37,139
[SPEAKER_01] po strane doći do toga

691
01:06:37,139 --> 01:06:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] da imaju odnos sa samim sobom

692
01:06:39,179 --> 01:06:41,219
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ako dođu, na primjer, na terapiju

693
01:06:41,219 --> 01:06:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] ili na nekakav,

694
01:06:41,980 --> 01:06:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] ono, sa nekom osobom koja će im to osvijesiti,

695
01:06:45,159 --> 01:06:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] hej, jesi primijetio da svaki put

696
01:06:46,980 --> 01:06:48,099
[SPEAKER_01] kad spominješ sebe,

697
01:06:48,099 --> 01:06:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] koristiš ove atribute

698
01:06:50,539 --> 01:06:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] ili što misliš o sebi to,

699
01:06:52,679 --> 01:06:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] kad malo to

700
01:06:53,940 --> 01:06:55,860
[SPEAKER_01] razdanimo,

701
01:06:56,940 --> 01:06:58,480
[SPEAKER_01] onda će postati svjesniji.

